snippets.title: AttachedClusters importAttachedCluster Sample
snippets.description: Imports creates a new [AttachedCluster][google.cloud.gkemulticloud.v1.AttachedCluster] resource by importing an existing Fleet Membership resource. If successful, the response contains a newly created [Operation][google.longrunning.Operation] resource that can be described to track the status of the operation.

snippets.title: AttachedClusters rollbackAwsNodePoolUpdate Sample
snippets.description: Rolls back a previously aborted or failed [AwsNodePool][google.cloud.gkemulticloud.v1.AwsNodePool] update request. Makes no changes if the last update request successfully finished. If an update request is in progress, you cannot rollback the update. You must first cancel or let it finish unsuccessfully before you can rollback.
